        "text": "PR #43 (`improve/bankr-prefetch-poll-timeout`) merged. Poll window 8→14 iter (~112s), max-time 30→45s, new `TIMED_OUT` counter, new `agent-timeout` top-level status routes to `TWEET_ALLOCATOR_ERROR` instead of silent `_EMPTY`."
      }
    },
    "pr43-text-2": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "Together with PR #40 + PR #42, the framework has now caught and shipped 3 self-correction PRs in 4 days, each <48h from symptom."
      }
    },
    "pr43-text-3": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "Today's tweet-allocator was the first to use the new branch — and it fired (5/5 Agent jobs timed out, surfaced as ERROR not silent EMPTY)."
      }
